{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DpNDCcWJG9MBzPZXxHgVR9","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# main.go\n2\t\n3\tPurpose: Entry point for the platform binary — instantiates the metrics and IAM HTTP handlers and starts each on its own port concurrently.\n4\tThe metrics service listens on :8081 and the IAM service on :8082. A fatal log terminates the process if either server fails to bind.\n5\t\n6\tTags: main\n7\t\n8\t## Public API\n9\t\n10\tThis file defines only `main`; there is no exported API.\n11\t\n12\t## Key Internals\n13\t\n14\t### `main()`\n15\t\n16\t```go\n17\tfunc main()\n18\t```\n19\t\n20\tCalls `metrics.New()` and `iam.New()` to obtain their respective `http.Handler` implementations, then launches the metrics server in a goroutine so both servers run concurrently. The IAM server runs on the main goroutine; a fatal error from either server terminates the process.\n21\t\n22\t## Dependencies\n23\t\n24\t| Package | Role |\n25\t|---------|------|\n26\t| `github.com/cornjacket/platform/internal/iam` | Provides the IAM HTTP handler via `iam.New()` |\n27\t| `github.com/cornjacket/platform/internal/metrics` | Provides the metrics HTTP handler via `metrics.New()` |\n28\t| `log` (stdlib) | Startup logging and fatal error reporting |\n29\t| `net/http` (stdlib) | `http.ListenAndServe` for both servers |\n30\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"70c03b5c-a214-4ae0-8a5a-e73f76e974f8","uuid":"b78608d1-cb9a-4fcb-af8c-b915bdf79935","timestamp":"2026-04-05T22:26:35.654Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/david/Go/src/github.com/cornjacket/ai-builder/establish-regression-recordings/sandbox/regressions/doc-platform-monolith/output/cmd/platform/main.go.md","content":"# main.go\n\nPurpose: Entry point for the platform binary — instantiates the metrics and IAM HTTP handlers and starts each on its own port concurrently.\nThe metrics service listens on :8081 and the IAM service on :8082. A fatal log terminates the process if either server fails to bind.\n\nTags: main\n\n## Public API\n\nThis file defines only `main`; there is no exported API.\n\n## Key Internals\n\n### `main()`\n\n```go\nfunc main()\n```\n\nCalls `metrics.New()` and `iam.New()` to obtain their respective `http.Handler` implementations, then launches the metrics server in a goroutine so both servers run concurrently. The IAM server runs on the main goroutine; a fatal error from either server terminates the process.\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Package | Role |\n|---------|------|\n| `github.com/cornjacket/platform/internal/iam` | Provides the IAM HTTP handler via `iam.New()` |\n| `github.com/cornjacket/platform/internal/metrics` | Provides the metrics HTTP handler via `metrics.New()` |\n| `log` (stdlib) | Startup logging and fatal error reporting |\n| `net/http` (stdlib) | `http.ListenAndServe` for both servers |\n","numLines":30,"startLine":1,"totalLines":30}}}
